      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">The Maestro's Resume Does Not Exist Yet</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">The most important role in AI is not on any job board. No university teaches it. No resume format captures it. Companies are hiring engineers when they should be hiring operators.</p>
